BUG-005

Module:
Search field

Environment:
Application: OWASP Juice Shop
Browser: Google Chrome
Operating System: Windows 11

Description:
The search text remains in the search field even after navigating to another page, which may confuse users.

Preconditions:
User is logged into the application.
Search bar is accessible.

Steps to Reproduce:
Open the Juice Shop application.
Search for Apple.
Navigate to another page (e.g., Basket or Contact Us).
Return to the Home page.

Expected Result:
The search field should be cleared when navigating away or returning to the Home page.

Actual Result:
The previous search keyword remains in the search field.

Severity:
Low

Priority:
Low
